== German ==

=== Etymology ===

From ''[[verbessern]]'' "to improve", ''[[verschlimmern]]'' "to make worse".

=== Verb ===

'''verschlimmbessern''' ([[verschlimmbesserte]], [[verschlimmbessert]])

# to make something worse in an honest but failed attempt to improve it; to [[disimprove]]

